Package: UltraGBIF
Title: Fast and Easy Compilation of GBIF Plant Occurrence Records in One R Package 
Version: 3.3.1
Date: 2026-04-13
Type: Package
Maintainer: Anonymous <Anonymous@Anonymous.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Anonymous", email = "Anonymous@Anonymous.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: GBIF hosts over 3 billion occurrence records. However, dealing with them typically involves lots of workflows and runtime, posing significant challenges for researchers. To address these limitations, we present UltraGBIF, a fast and easy R package to parse and merge enormous GBIF occurrence records.
